#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/units/dark-mage.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Although Malin's sword has grown rusty from lack of proper care, his "
"increasing skill with magic more than compensates.\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
